{"tid":1561272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係團結嘅 就係黨鐵站做哨兵 反制班捉跳閘狗","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:14:27.000Z","uid":79161,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b62376c244c600ade7cd308d56cee298239b95bb","tid":1561272,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"班食訓痾就滿足嘅廢老、警犬、foodpanda<br />\n咁得閒棟係黨鐵捉手足<br />\n其實只要夠人圍佢地 就幫到手足甩身架喇<br />\n所以街坊得閒就做哨兵<br />\n若無其事咁係閘口「接放學」<br />\n當有賣港藍絲想陷害手足<br />\n大家就立即反制佢地 叫tg或者街坊幫手圍佢<br />\n撚到佢哋懷疑人生<br />\n點解跳閘都有咁多人撐 自己先係異類<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁做好似墮入咗民鬥嘅共狗奸計<br />\n但係只要頭幾次做得好<br />\n教訓到班賣港藍絲<br />\n有阻嚇作用 將來佢哋就唔敢咁猖狂"},{"pid":"8a38847a91517f98aba07f99a556540fdefb5c86","tid":1561272,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4913e6819786a00ee6beef61514a73acb496c1df","tid":1561272,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e79edbf7a1a54d8b7e09596ccb7992f899aedf","tid":1561272,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/